title: マチタンのむんむんデー

text_block_list.name: Nice Nature
text_block_list.text: Wheeeeeew...! Tannhauser, you're really energetic today~.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Yeah. Today's a little special... It's 'Mun-Day'.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: 'Mun-Day' is when my family's shop has free service menu items. Like meatballs, or fried chicken.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Mun~, I was super busy helping out too. On bargain days of the week, mmm! My body just gets all fired up on its own.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: So that's why... today, I'm gonna do extra training too!

text_block_list.name: Nice Nature
text_block_list.text: Hey hey, don't push yourself too hard...!

text_block_list.name: Nice Nature
text_block_list.text: ...I can't see you anymore. 'Mmm-Day' is fearsome...
Matikanetannhauser was more fired up than usual, and after running, she seemed to have even tackled extra menu items.

text_block_list.name: Nice Nature
text_block_list.text: Watch out, there! The ground's sunken in!
